PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-89 of January 11, 1995, which appointed MICHEL FOURNIER as a member of the St. Lawrence Seaway Authority by revoking the words "for a term of two years" and substituting the words "for a term ending July 10, 1997, or if the Authority is dissolved before the expiry of this term, upon dissolution of the Authority".
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1995-89 of January 11, 1995, which
appointed MICHEL FOURNIER as a member of the St. Lawrence Seaway
Authority by revoking the words "for a term of two years" and
substituting the words "for a term ending July 10, 1997, or if the
Authority is dissolved before the expiry of this term, upon dissolution
of the Authority".
